      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i tried the \"digital detox\" thing but it doesnt change the reality. the reality is just so heavy. i look at my plans, my career, even just thinking about having kids or growing old, and it all just feels like a joke. why bother building anything, or even being here, if it's all just going to burn up or drown anyway? it feels like we're just delaying the inevitable.",
